Interface DLCore

All Superinterfaces:
DLEntity
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseDLCore, DefaultCore
public interface DLCore extends DLEntity
A core is not intended to be used to parse in multiple threads!
Author:
Benjamin Schiller
